{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_20260226003858f91ea70b378a43de","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-5","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the actual methods in LibraryTracker:\n- addBook(Book book)\n- findByIsbn(String isbn) \n- borrowBook(String isbn, String borrower)\n- returnBook(String isbn, String borrower)\n- hasBorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower)\n- listAllBooks()\n- removeBook(String isbn)\n- getBookCount()\n\nMethods that DON'T exist (mentioned in ASSIGNMENT.md):\n- `findBook(String isbn)` - should be `findByIsbn`\n- `hasBook(String isbn)` - doesn't exist\n- `getBorrowRecordsByUser(String borrower)` - doesn't exist\n- `getAllBorrowRecords()` - doesn't exist\n\nLet me fix ASSIGNMENT.md:\n1. Line 8: Change deadline from 2026-02-15 to a reasonable future date\n2. Line 37: `findBook` → `findByIsbn`\n3. Line 39: Remove `hasBook(String isbn)`\n4. Lines 43-44: Remove `getBorrowRecordsByUser` and `getAllBorrowRecords`, replace with `hasBorrowRecord`\n5. Line 168: `findBook` → `findByIsbn`\n6. Line 186: `findBook` → `findByIsbn`","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"71156586-c7e3-42b6-afb9-166ae181c2a1","uuid":"b58fdb3b-460c-4b11-ab40-adbd71fa2c59"}
